  "Description": {
    "English": "A powerful but mellow <span class=\"name name-technology\">musical instrument</span>, capable of relaying song through space via gently undulating electromagnetic waves.<br><br>Use Relay Song (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>) while in <span class=\"name name-special\">deep space</span> to broadcast the flute's melody...",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个强大但是声音柔和的<span class=\"name name-technology\">乐器</span>，可以通过轻轻起伏的电磁波向太空中播放音乐。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-special\">深空中</span>使用中继音乐播放器（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）广播长笛的旋律......",
    "TraditionalChinese": "強大但聲調柔和的<span class=\"name name-technology\">樂器</span>，能夠透過起伏平緩的電磁波，在太空中傳遞歌曲。<br><br>身處<span class=\"name name-special\">深空</span>時使用傳遞歌曲 (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)，播送長笛的旋律......"
  },
